OL,3,CWhere Christmas jumpers are made:
OL,4,CInside Santa's knitwear workshop
OL,6,FLove them or loathe them, Christmas
OL,7,Fjumpers are undoubtedly a trend that
OL,8,Fkeeps coming back every festive
OL,9,Fseason, growing in popularity year on
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FHundreds of thousands of festive knits
OL,13,Fare made at factories across the UK
OL,14,Fevery year.
OL,16,FJack Masters' jumper factory in
OL,17,FLeicester has been making knitwear in
OL,18,Fthe city since 1987 and in 2010 the
OL,19,Ffirm spotted a gap in the market and
OL,20,Fbranched into making seasonal sweaters
OL,21,Ftoo.
