OL,3,CWhere Christmas jumpers are made:
OL,4,CInside Santa's knitwear workshop
OL,6,FThey've been so popular that they now
OL,7,Fmake up around 20% of all their
OL,8,Fproduction. They estimate to have made
OL,9,Faround #250,000 over the past 14 years.
OL,11,FTheir Christmas brand, British
OL,12,FChristmas Jumpers, provides
OL,13,Fpersonalised jumpers to firms
OL,14,Fincluding Google, and even makes
OL,15,Fdesigns for the Houses of Parliament
OL,16,Fgift shop.
OL,18,FIt's like Santa's very own workshop
OL,19,Fall year round at the factory, with
OL,20,FChristmas jumpers in production from
OL,21,FJanuary to December.
