OL,3,CWhere Christmas jumpers are made:
OL,4,CInside Santa's knitwear workshop
OL,6,FDirector, Snahal Patal explains: "We
OL,7,Fsaw in 2010 a bit of a trend for
OL,8,FChristmas jumpers from the US. It
OL,9,Fseemed to be getting a little more
OL,10,Fpopular.
OL,12,F"We thought, why don't we start so we
OL,13,Fdesigned 10 jumpers within the space
OL,14,Fof 2-3 weeks.
OL,16,F"We started a website and we ended up
OL,17,Fselling around 3,000 units in our
OL,18,Ffirst year."
