OL,3,CWhere Christmas jumpers are made:
OL,4,CInside Santa's knitwear workshop
OL,6,FThe family business employs around 35
OL,7,Fmembers of staff, some have been at
OL,8,Fthe company for around 25 years.
OL,10,FThe staff are all highly skilled, but
OL,11,Fin order to protect the craft for the
OL,12,Ffuture, the firm's keen to attract
OL,13,Fmore youngsters onto the factory floor.
