OL,3,CWhere Christmas jumpers are made:
OL,4,CInside Santa's knitwear workshop
OL,6,FSnahal said: "It's very hard to
OL,7,Freplace the skills, sewing is a skill,
OL,8,Fknitting is a skill, programming is a
OL,9,Fskill. So we do need young people to
OL,10,Fcome into this industry otherwise
OL,11,Fthere will be nothing left and I think
OL,12,Fthe knitwear trade, there's a handful
OL,13,Fof knitwear factories left in the UK.
OL,15,FDespite the decline in trade here in
OL,16,Fthe UK, demand for Christmas knitwear
OL,17,Fremains, and at the Jack Masters
OL,18,Ffactory, sustainability is at the
OL,19,Fheart of production.
