OL,3,CWhere Christmas jumpers are made:
OL,4,CInside Santa's knitwear workshop
OL,6,FDesigner Rosa Hutchesson said: "For
OL,7,Four Christmas jumpers the main fabric
OL,8,Fwe use is made from a mixture of
OL,9,Fblended, recycled cotton and crushed
OL,10,Fup plastic bottles to create recycled
OL,11,Fpolyester, so a blend of the two of
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"By using this instead of pure virgin
OL,15,Fcotton we are saving around 2,700
OL,16,Flitres of water per jumper."
