OL,3,CWhere Christmas jumpers are made:
OL,4,CInside Santa's knitwear workshop
OL,6,FSnahal said that over the past five
OL,7,Fyears they have noticed a trend for
OL,8,Fmore niche, personalised Christmas
OL,9,Fjumpers, but admits their most popular
OL,10,Fdesigns this year is their festive
OL,11,FChristmas dinner classic, featuring
OL,12,Fall the trimmings; turkey, pigs in
OL,13,Fblankets, sprouts and crackers.
OL,15,FDesigners have already started working
OL,16,Fon 2025's creations, which are soon to
OL,17,Fenter the production line.
